OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 20 May to Fri 29 May
OL,6,FChangeable conditions are expected at
OL,7,Ffirst, with low pressure often close
OL,8,Fby to the north of the UK, bringing
OL,9,Frain and showers. However, high
OL,10,Fpressure from the south is expected to
OL,11,Fquickly start to build near to the UK
OL,12,Ftowards the Bank Holiday weekend,
OL,13,Fbringing some fine and dry conditions,
OL,14,Fwith temperatures rising accordingly
OL,15,Ffor some. Thereafter, high pressure is
OL,16,Fexpected to broadly remain the
OL,17,Fdominant influence across much of the
OL,18,FUK, with spells of fine weather. Low
OL,19,Fpressure will be positioned to the
OL,20,Fnorth, and will at times allow some
OL,21,Frain or showers to cross the country.
OL,22,FOverall across the period,
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Ftemperatures are expected to be above
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fnormal with winds often light for many.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
