PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1778854269
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 30 May to Sat 13 Jun
OL,6,FWhilst further rain and showers are
OL,7,Fpossible at times, there is also
OL,8,Flikely to be spells of fine and dry
OL,9,Fweather. Patterns which bring more
OL,10,Fsettled weather are more likely to
OL,11,Fdominate through the turn of the month
OL,12,Facross southern areas with more
OL,13,Funsettled spells of weather likely to
OL,14,Fbe focused further north. Into June,
OL,15,Fmore mixed conditions are likely with
OL,16,Fspells of rain and showers, but also
OL,17,Fsome drier weather at times.
OL,18,FTemperatures are most likely to be
OL,19,Fnear or slightly above average
OL,20,Foverall, with some warm weather
OL,21,Fpossible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
